  "translations": {
    "en": "Muhammad ibn Zakariyya al-Ghilabi said: I asked Shu'ayb al-Muzani about the length of this report, and he said to me: O Abu Abdillah, I asked al-Husayn ibn Zayd about the length of this hadith, and he said: Ja'far ibn Muhammad ibn Ali ibn al-Husayn ibn Ali ibn Abi Talib (peace be upon them) narrated to me that he compiled this hadith from the book that was dictated by the Messenger of Allah (peace be upon him and his family) and written in the hand of Ali ibn Abi Talib (peace be upon him).",
